uh that's the that's the uh underlying philosophy should we say that's driving him to practice these uh self these um mortifications renunciation is letting go of attachment to something so it's not as though you you stop eating you just try to distinguish between the desire which is coming from ordinary appetite from the desire which is seeking happiness in in food so which is a completely different idea yeah

